(10, 'com_content.article.3', '', '2023-04-01 11:10:27', 570, 5517, 'f2996af1208a13384bd83c231bb64e94395bf2c9', '{\"id\":3,\"asset_id\":99,\"title\":\"Kinh nghi\\u1ec7m Marketing Online 1: T\\u1ed1i \\u01b0u tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m tr\\u00ean website\",\"alias\":\"kinh-nghi-m-marketing-online-1-t-i-uu-tr-i-nghi-m-tren-website\",\"introtext\":\"<h2><span id=\\\"Kinh_nghiem_Marketing_Online_1_Toi_uu_trai_nghiem_tren_website\\\"><strong>Kinh nghi\\u1ec7m Marketing Online 1: T\\u1ed1i \\u01b0u tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m tr\\u00ean website<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc h\\u1ebft, n\\u1ebfu b\\u1ea1n c\\u1ed1 g\\u1eafng k\\u00e9o th\\u1eadt nhi\\u1ec1u kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng v\\u00e0o website nh\\u01b0ng tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u00f3 l\\u1ea1i k\\u00e9m s\\u1ebd g\\u00e2y ra nh\\u1eefng t\\u1ed5n th\\u1ea5t n\\u1eb7ng n\\u1ec1 cho b\\u1ea1n.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>B\\u1ea1n b\\u1ecf nhi\\u1ec1u ng\\u00e2n s\\u00e1ch qu\\u1ea3ng c\\u00e1o \\u0111\\u1eb7t link v\\u1ec1 website v\\u00e0 sau khi h\\u1ecd v\\u00e0o, h\\u1ecd l\\u1ea1i tho\\u00e1t ra m\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng h\\u1ec1 c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t h\\u00e0nh \\u0111\\u1ed9ng li\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 mua h\\u00e0ng. C\\u00f3 ph\\u1ea3i b\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang l\\u00e3ng ph\\u00ed hay kh\\u00f4ng?<\\/p>\\r\\n<figure id=\\\"attachment_11134\\\" class=\\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\\" aria-describedby=\\\"caption-attachment-11134\\\"><img class=\\\"wp-image-11134\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/gobranding.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/chia-se-kinh-nghiem-marketing-online-lay-website-lam-trung-tam-toi-uu-trai-nghiem-nguoi-dung.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"600\\\" height=\\\"398\\\" loading=\\\"lazy\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<figcaption id=\\\"caption-attachment-11134\\\" class=\\\"wp-caption-text\\\">T\\u1ed1i \\u01b0u tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m tr\\u00ean website l\\u00e0 h\\u1ea1ng m\\u1ee5c c\\u1ef1c k\\u1ef3 quan tr\\u1ecdng.<\\/figcaption>\\r\\n<\\/figure>\\r\\n<p>Tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00f9ng tr\\u00ean website r\\u1ea5t quan tr\\u1ecdng. T\\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ed9 t\\u1ea3i trang l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t v\\u00ed d\\u1ee5 \\u0111i\\u1ec3n h\\u00ecnh!<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Theo m\\u1ed9t kh\\u1ea3o s\\u00e1t c\\u1ee7a Akamai v\\u00e0 Gomez.com, n\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ed9 t\\u1ea3i trang v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t qu\\u00e1 3 gi\\u00e2y s\\u1ebd c\\u00f3 t\\u1edbi 79% b\\u1ecf \\u0111i. Trong s\\u1ed1 b\\u1ecf \\u0111i n\\u00e0y, c\\u00f3 80% cho bi\\u1ebft h\\u1ecd s\\u1ebd kh\\u00f4ng quay l\\u1ea1i website \\u0111\\u00f3 n\\u1eefa. H\\u01a1n th\\u1ebf n\\u1eefa, c\\u00f3 44% s\\u1ebd chia s\\u1ebb \\u201ctr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m kh\\u00f3 ch\\u1ecbu khi mua s\\u1eafm\\u201d cho b\\u1ea1n b\\u00e8 v\\u00e0 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi th\\u00e2n.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>D\\u01b0\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 y\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed1 c\\u01a1 b\\u1ea3n b\\u1ea1n c\\u1ea7n ch\\u00fa \\u00fd trong qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00f9ng tr\\u00ean website:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Giao di\\u1ec7n website: \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n, r\\u00f5 r\\u00e0ng, kh\\u00f4ng qu\\u00e1 r\\u01b0\\u1eddm r\\u00e0 v\\u00e0 nhi\\u1ec1u chi ti\\u1ebft.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Th\\u00e2n thi\\u1ec7n v\\u1edbi thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb di \\u0111\\u1ed9ng: t\\u1ed1i \\u01b0u tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m tr\\u00ean mobile.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng h\\u00ecnh \\u1ea3nh: r\\u00f5 n\\u00e9t, c\\u00f3 li\\u00ean quan \\u0111\\u1ebfn n\\u1ed9i dung.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>T\\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ed9 load trang: n\\u00ean \\u00edt h\\u01a1n 2 gi\\u00e2y.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Ti\\u1ebfn tr\\u00ecnh thanh to\\u00e1n online: nhanh ch\\u00f3ng v\\u00e0 li\\u00ean k\\u1ebft v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c c\\u1ed5ng thanh to\\u00e1n ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>V\\u1ecb tr\\u00ed \\u0111\\u1eb7t c\\u00e1c th\\u00f4ng th\\u00f4ng tin li\\u00ean l\\u1ea1c: d\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng t\\u00ecm th\\u1ea5y th\\u00f4ng tin li\\u00ean l\\u1ea1c ngay khi kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng c\\u1ea7n.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>C\\u00e1ch \\u0111i\\u1ec1u h\\u01b0\\u1edbng lu\\u1ed3ng n\\u1ed9i dung: gi\\u00fap kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng d\\u1ec5 t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm th\\u00f4ng tin v\\u00e0 l\\u01b0u l\\u1ea1i tr\\u00ean website l\\u00e2u h\\u01a1n.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>S\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng b\\u1ed9 trong thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf: font ch\\u1eef, size ch\\u1eef, m\\u00e0u s\\u1eafc,\\u2026<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":9,\"created\":\"2023-04-01 11:10:27\",\"created_by\":570,\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-04-01 11:10:27\",\"modified_by\":570,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2023-04-01 11:10:27\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"https:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/gobranding.com.vn\\\\\\/dich-vu-toi-uu-toc-do-website\\\\\\/\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_no