(24, 'com_content.article.8', '', '2023-04-02 14:54:38', 570, 4799, 'c1c6dd726a26a7b2604dddf40eae2c89dc8b860d', '{\"id\":8,\"asset_id\":104,\"title\":\"Kinh nghi\\u1ec7m Marketing Online 4: Gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u website tr\\u00ean m\\u1ecdi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac online\",\"alias\":\"kinh-nghi-m-marketing-online-4-gi-i-thi-u-website-tren-m-i-di-m-ti-p-xuc-online\",\"introtext\":\"<h2><span id=\\\"Kinh_nghiem_Marketing_Online_4_Gioi_thieu_website_tren_moi_diem_tiep_xuc_online\\\"><strong>Kinh nghi\\u1ec7m Marketing Online 4: Gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u website tr\\u00ean m\\u1ecdi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac online<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>B\\u1ea1n mu\\u1ed1n kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng v\\u00e0o t\\u00ecm hi\\u1ec3u s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c n\\u1ed9i dung tr\\u00ean website? V\\u1eady h\\u00e3y c\\u00f4ng khai \\u0111\\u1ecba ch\\u1ec9 website tr\\u00ean t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 c\\u00e1c k\\u00eanh ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac v\\u1edbi kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng. C\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u1ecba ch\\u1ec9 website s\\u1ebd mang l\\u1ea1i h\\u00ecnh \\u1ea3nh chuy\\u00ean nghi\\u1ec7p v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u00e1ng tin c\\u1eady h\\u01a1n cho doanh nghi\\u00eap. \\u0110\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t l\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c m\\u1eb7t h\\u00e0ng c\\u00f3 gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb cao.<\\/p>\\r\\n<figure id=\\\"attachment_11137\\\" class=\\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\\" aria-describedby=\\\"caption-attachment-11137\\\"><img class=\\\"wp-image-11137\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/gobranding.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/chia-se-kinh-nghiem-marketing-online-lay-website-lam-trung-tam-cong-khai-dia-chi-trang-web-1024x480.png\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/gobranding.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/chia-se-kinh-nghiem-marketing-online-lay-website-lam-trung-tam-cong-khai-dia-chi-trang-web-1024x480.png 1024w, https:\\/\\/gobranding.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/chia-se-kinh-nghiem-marketin