(26, 'com_content.article.9', '', '2023-04-02 14:55:34', 570, 5446, '1b0d1fe0f75c0f47c40dc18c23b6813ce6bb14cf', '{\"id\":\"9\",\"asset_id\":105,\"title\":\"Kinh nghi\\u1ec7m Marketing Online 5: Chia s\\u1ebb n\\u1ed9i dung \\u201c\\u0111\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u00e1o\\u201d tr\\u00ean website cho c\\u00e1c k\\u00eanh kh\\u00e1c\",\"alias\":\"kinh-nghi-m-marketing-online-5-chia-s-n-i-dung-d-c-dao-tren-website-cho-cac-kenh-khac\",\"introtext\":\"<h2><span id=\\\"Kinh_nghiem_Marketing_Online_5_Chia_se_noi_dung_doc_dao_tren_website_cho_cac_kenh_khac\\\"><strong>Kinh nghi\\u1ec7m Marketing Online 5: Chia s\\u1ebb n\\u1ed9i dung \\u201c\\u0111\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u00e1o\\u201d tr\\u00ean website cho c\\u00e1c k\\u00eanh kh\\u00e1c<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<figure id=\\\"attachment_11138\\\" class=\\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\\" aria-describedby=\\\"caption-attachment-11138\\\"><img class=\\\"wp-image-11138\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/gobranding.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/chia-se-kinh-nghiem-marketing-online-lay-website-lam-trung-tam-share-noi-dung-len-mang-xa-hoi.png\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/gobranding.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/chia-se-kinh-nghiem-marketing-online-lay-website-lam-trung-tam-share-noi-dung-len-mang-xa-hoi.png 642w, https:\\/\\/gobranding.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/chia-se-kinh-nghiem-marketing-online-lay-website-lam-trung-tam-share-noi-dung-len-mang-xa-hoi-600x500.png 600w\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"600\\\" height=\\\"500\\\" loading=\\\"lazy\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<figcaption id=\\\"caption-attachment-11138\\\" class=\\\"wp-caption-text\\\">H\\u00e3y chia s\\u1ebb n\\u1ed9i dung m\\u1edbi tr\\u00ean website l\\u00ean m\\u1ea1ng x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i.<\\/figcaption>\\r\\n<\\/figure>\\r\\n<p>B\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u00e3 t\\u1ed1n nhi\\u1ec1u c\\u00f4ng s\\u1ee9c \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nhi\\u1ec1u n\\u1ed9i dung s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o m\\u1edbi tr\\u00ean website? V\\u1eady th\\u00ec th\\u1eadt u\\u1ed5ng ph\\u00ed khi kh\\u00f4ng truy\\u1ec1n th\\u00f4ng ch\\u00fang tr\\u00ean c\\u00e1c k\\u00eanh Marketing Online kh\\u00e1c (M\\u1ea1ng X\\u00e3 H\\u1ed9i, Email Marketing, di\\u1ec5n \\u0111\\u00e0n,\\u2026) m\\u00e0 b\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu. B\\u1ea1n s\\u1ebd b\\u1ea5t ng\\u1edd r\\u1eb1ng, ch\\u1ec9 v\\u1edbi 1 n\\u1ed9i dung tr\\u00ean website b\\u1ea1n ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o ra nhi\\u1ec1u d\\u1ea1ng th\\u1ee9c tr\\u00ecnh b\\u00e0y tr\\u00ean \\u0111a k\\u00eanh ti\\u1ebfp th\\u1ecb.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em>V\\u00ed d\\u1ee5 nh\\u01b0 tr\\u00ean Fanpage Facebook, ngo\\u00e0i c\\u00e1c h\\u00ecnh \\u1ea3nh v\\u00e0 n\\u1ed9i dung t\\u1ee9c th\\u1eddi, b\\u1ea1n h\\u00e3y chia s\\u1ebb th\\u00eam c\\u00e1c b\\u00e0i vi\\u1ebft\\u00a0m\\u1edbi\\u00a0xu\\u1ea5t b\\u1ea3n tr\\u00ean website. Nh\\u01b0 v\\u1eady, b\\u1ea1n v\\u1eeba t\\u0103ng kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn c\\u1ee7a n\\u1ed9i dung m\\u1edbi, v\\u1eeba gi\\u00fap t\\u0103ng \\u0111i\\u1ec3m \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 c\\u1ee7a Google cho website nh\\u1edd v\\u00e0o s\\u1ef1 chia s\\u1ebb tr\\u00ean c\\u00e1c k\\u00eanh kh\\u00e1c.<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em>T\\u01b0\\u01a1ng t\\u1ef1, b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 d\\u00f9ng n\\u1ed9i dung m\\u1edbi tr\\u00ean website \\u0111\\u1ec3 g\\u1eedi Email Marketing v\\u1edbi m\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u00edch ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng. Lo\\u1ea1i n\\u1ed9i dung n\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 d\\u1ec5 t\\u1ea1o thi\\u1ec7n c\\u1ea3m h\\u01a1n so v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c Email c\\u00f3 n\\u1ed9i dung mang t\\u00ednh ch\\u1ea5t b\\u00e1n h\\u00e0ng. \\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi, n\\u00f3 c\\u0169ng gi\\u00fap b\\u1ea1n t\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng truy c\\u1eadp cho website, h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 h\\u1eefu \\u00edch cho SEO.<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Hy v\\u1ecdng v\\u1edbi 5 kinh nghi\\u1ec7m Marketing Online l\\u1ea5y website l\\u00e0m trung t\\u00e2m, b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u201cao nh\\u00e0\\u201d \\u0111\\u1ee7 l\\u1edbn \\u0111\\u1ec3 thu h\\u00fat, d\\u1eabn d\\u1eaft kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ebfn ng\\u00e0y c\\u00e0ng nhi\\u1ec1u h\\u01a1n, h\\u01b0\\u1edbng \\u0111\\u1ebfn s\\u1ef1 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n b\\u1ec1n v\\u1eefng.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":9,\"created\":\"2023-04-02 14:54:59\",\"created_by\":\"570\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-04-02 14:55:34\",\"modified_by\":570,\"checked_out\":570,\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-04-02 14:55:29\",\"publish_up\":\"2023-04-02 14:54:59\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":2,\"ordering\":0,\"metakey\":\"Kinh nghi\\u1ec7m Marketing\",\"metadesc\":\"Kinh nghi\\u1ec7m Marketing\",\"access\":1,\"hits\":0,\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0),
(27, 'com_content.article.8', '', '2023-04-02 14:55:47', 570, 4814, '29723412fe3240480fd0a377ee85003773c8be07', '{\"id\":\"8\",\"asset_id\":104,\"title\":\"Kinh nghi\\u1ec7m Marketing Online 4: Gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u website tr\\u00ean m\\u1ecdi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac online\",\"alias\":\"kinh-nghi-m-marketing-online-4-gi-i-thi-u-website-tren-m-i-di-m-ti-p-xuc-online\",\"introtext\":\"<h2><span id=\\\"Kinh_nghiem_Marketing_Online_4_Gioi_thieu_website_tren_moi_diem_tiep_xuc_online\\\"><strong>Kinh nghi\\u1ec7m Marketing Online 4: Gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u website tr\\u00ean m\\u1ecdi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac online<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>B\\u1ea1n mu\\u1ed1n kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng v\\u00e0o t\\u00ecm hi\\u1ec3u s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c n\\u1ed9i dung tr\\u00ean website? V\\u1eady h\\u00e3y c\\u00f4ng khai \\u0111\\u1ecba ch\\u1ec9 website tr\\u00ean t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 c\\u00e1c k\\u00eanh ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac v\\u1edbi kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng. C\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u1ecba ch\\u1ec9 website s\\u1ebd mang l\\u1ea1i h\\u00ecnh \\u1ea3nh chuy\\u00ean nghi\\u1ec7p v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u00e1ng tin c\\u1eady h\\u01a1n cho doanh nghi\\u00eap. \\u0110\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t l\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c m\\u1eb7t h\\u00e0ng c\\u00f3 gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb cao.<\\/p>\\r\\n<figure id=\\\"attachment_11137\\\" class=\\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\\" aria-describedby=\\\"caption-attachment-11137\\\"><img class=\\\"wp-image-11137\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/gobranding.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/chia-se-kinh-nghiem-marketing-online-lay-website-lam-trung-tam-cong-khai-dia-chi-trang-web-1024x480.png\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/gobranding.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/chia-se-kinh-nghiem-marketing-online-lay-website-lam-trung-tam-cong-khai-dia-chi-trang-web-1024x480.png 1024w, https:\\/\\/gobranding.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/chia-se-kinh-nghiem-mark