(28, 'com_content.article.7', '', '2023-04-02 14:56:01', 570, 5860, '014c485610cd1e80080ed7c670a3f1e3f182c02f', '{\"id\":\"7\",\"asset_id\":103,\"title\":\"Kinh nghi\\u1ec7m Marketing Online 3: Khi\\u1ebfn h\\u00e0ng ngh\\u00ecn kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng th\\u1ea5y website khi search Google\",\"alias\":\"kinh-nghi-m-marketing-online-3-khi-n-hang-nghin-khach-hang-th-y-website-khi-search-google\",\"introtext\":\"<h2><span id=\\\"Kinh_nghiem_Marketing_Online_3_Khien_hang_nghin_khach_hang_thay_website_khi_search_Google\\\"><strong>Kinh nghi\\u1ec7m Marketing Online 3: Khi\\u1ebfn h\\u00e0ng ngh\\u00ecn kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng th\\u1ea5y website khi search Google<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>GOBRANDING tin r\\u1eb1ng ngay c\\u1ea3 b\\u1ea1n c\\u0169ng hay d\\u00f9ng Google \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm c\\u00e1c th\\u00f4ng tin c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft. V\\u00e0 kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 v\\u1eady. Trung b\\u00ecnh m\\u1ed7i gi\\u00e2y, c\\u00f3 t\\u1edbi 40.000 l\\u01b0\\u1ee3t t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm (t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u01a1ng 3,5 t\\u1ef7 l\\u01b0\\u1ee3t t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm m\\u1ed7i ng\\u00e0y).<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>N\\u1ebfu b\\u1ea1n b\\u1ecf qua hay \\u201cl\\u1ee1\\u201d qu\\u00ean m\\u1ea5t k\\u00eanh kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng n\\u00e0y, b\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang \\u0111\\u00e1nh m\\u1ea5t c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i t\\u0103ng doanh thu v\\u00f4 c\\u00f9ng b\\u00e9o b\\u1edf!<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>C\\u00f3 2 c\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u1ec3 website c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n xu\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n tr\\u00ean trang \\u0111\\u1ea7u c\\u1ee7a Google:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Google Adwords<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>SEO<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>V\\u1edbi Google Adwords, b\\u1ea1n tr\\u1ea3 ti\\u1ec1n tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp cho Google \\u0111\\u1ec3 website xu\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ebfn ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm. Tuy nhi\\u00ean, khi d\\u1eebng tr\\u1ea3 ti\\u1ec1n, ngay l\\u1eadp t\\u1ee9c ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm kh\\u00f4ng h\\u1ec1 th\\u1ea5y website c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n n\\u1eefa.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>SEO th\\u00ec ng\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u1ea1i, b\\u1ea1n tr\\u1ea3 ti\\u1ec1n cho nh\\u00e2n vi\\u00ean SEO hay c\\u00f4ng ty d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 SEO. \\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi b\\u1ea1n c\\u1ea7n t\\u1ed1n nhi\\u1ec1u th\\u1eddi gian \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n d\\u1ea7n th\\u1ee9 h\\u1ea1ng ch\\u1ee9 kh\\u00f4ng xu\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n ngay tr\\u00ean trang nh\\u1ea5t nh\\u01b0 Adwords \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c. Nh\\u01b0ng b\\u00f9 l\\u1ea1i, khi b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u00e3 v\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c trang nh\\u1ea5t v\\u00e0 n\\u1ebfu d\\u1eebng SEO, website\\u00a0s\\u1ebd kh\\u00f4ng bi\\u1ebfn m\\u1ea5t ngay l\\u1eadp t\\u1ee9c m\\u00e0 th\\u1ee9 h\\u1ea1ng s\\u1ebd gi\\u1ea3m t\\u1eeb t\\u1eeb sang trang 2, trang 3,\\u2026<\\/p>\\r\\n<figure id=\\\"attachment_11136\\\" class=\\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\\" aria-describedby=\\\"caption-attachment-11136\\\"><img class=\\\"wp-image-11136\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/gobranding.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/chia-se-kinh-nghiem-marketing-online-lay-website-lam-trung-tam-lam-website-xuat-hien-tren-Google.png\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/gobranding.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/chia-se-kinh-nghiem-marketing-online-lay-website-lam-trung-tam-lam-website-xuat-hien-tren-Google.png 803w, https:\\/\\/gobranding.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/chia-se-kinh-nghiem-marketing-online-lay-website-lam-trung-tam-lam-website-xuat-hien-tren-Google-600x460.png 600w, https:\\/\\/gobranding.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/chia-se-kinh-nghiem-marketing-online-lay-website-lam-trung-tam-lam-website-xuat-hien-tren-Google-768x589.png 768w\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"600\\\" height=\\\"460\\\" loading=\\\"lazy\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<figcaption id=\\\"caption-attachment-11136\\\" class=\\\"wp-caption-text\\\">V\\u1ecb tr\\u00ed hi\\u1ec3n th\\u1ecb t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean tr\\u00ean trang nh\\u1ea5t Google nh\\u1edd SEO hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3.<\\/figcaption>\\r\\n<\\/figure>\\r\\n<p>Th\\u00eam m\\u1ed9t th\\u00f4ng tin c\\u1ef1c k\\u1ef3 h\\u1eefu \\u00edch cho b\\u1ea1n n\\u1eefa: Theo b\\u00e1o c\\u00e1o c\\u1ee7a Google, c\\u00f3 kho\\u1ea3ng 65% ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00f9ng ch\\u1ec9 click v\\u00e0o 10 v\\u1ecb tr\\u00ed t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean (v\\u1ecb tr\\u00ed c\\u1ee7a SEO). V\\u00e0 kho\\u1ea3ng 10% ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00f9ng ch\\u1ec9 click v\\u00e0o Adword. C\\u00f2n l\\u1ea1i c\\u00f3 kho\\u1ea3ng 25% ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00f9ng sau khi click v\\u00e0o qu\\u1ea3ng c\\u00e1o s\\u1ebd l\\u1ea1i ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c click v\\u00e0o k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":9,\"created\":\"2023-04-02 14:54:14\",\"created_by\":\"570\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-04-02 14:56:01\",\"modified_by\":570,\"checked_out\":570,\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-04-02 14:55:57\",\"publish_up\":\"2023-04-02 14:54:14\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":2,\"ordering\":2,\"metakey\":\"Kinh nghi\\u1ec7m Marketing\",\"metadesc\":\"Kinh nghi\\u1ec7m Marketing\",\"access\":1,\"hits\":0,\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0),
(29, 'com_content.article.6', '', '2023-04-02 14:56:12', 570, 6504, '5387ab3ab509a811f080410d4cc451ec4cdf935c', '{\"id\":\"6\",\"asset_id\":102,\"title\":\"Kinh nghi\\u1ec7m Marketing Online 2: Kh\\u00f4ng ng\\u1eebng x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng n\\u1ed9i dung \\u0111\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u00e1o tr\\u00ean website\",\"alias\":\"kinh-nghi-m-marketing-online-2-khong-ng-ng-xay-d-ng-n-i-dung-d-c-dao-tren-website\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Lang thang tr\\u00ean internet, b\\u1ea1n s\\u1ebd th\\u1ea5y c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 website ch\\u1ec9 to\\u00e0n n\\u1ed9i dung b\\u00e1n h\\u00e0ng. N\\u1ed9i dung tr\\u00ean trang web r\\u1ea5t \\u201cngh\\u00e8o n\\u00e0n\\u201d!<\\/p>\\r\\n<figure id=\\\"attachment_11135\\\" class=\\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\\" aria-describedby=\\\"caption-attachment-11135\\\"><img class=\\\"wp-image-11135\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/gobranding.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/chia-se-kinh-nghiem-marketing-online-lay-website-lam-trung-tam-cap-nhat-noi-dung-dinh-ky.jpg\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/gobranding.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/chia-se-kinh-nghiem-marketing-online-lay-website-lam-trung-tam-cap-nhat-noi-dung-dinh-ky.jpg 960w, https:\\/\\/gobranding.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/chia-se-kinh-nghiem-marketing-online-lay-website-lam-trung-tam-cap-nhat-noi-dung-dinh-ky-600x398.jpg 600w, https:\\/\\/gobranding.com.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/chia-se-kinh-nghiem-marketing-online-lay-website-lam-trung-tam-cap-nhat-noi-dung-dinh-ky-768x509.jpg 768w\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"600\\\" height=\\\"398\\\" loading=\\\"lazy\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<figcaption id=\\\"caption-attachment-11135\\\" class=\\\"wp-caption-text\\\">C\\u1eadp nh\\u1eadt n\\u1ed9i dung m\\u1edbi th\\u01b0\\u1eddng xuy\\u00ean gi\\u00fap \\u201cl\\u00e0m gi\\u00e0u\\u201d gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb website.<\\/figcaption>\\r\\n<\\/figure>\\r\\n<p>B\\u1ea1n ph\\u1ea3i kh\\u00f4ng ng\\u1eebng \\u201cl\\u00e0m gi\\u00e0u\\u201d cho website b\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1c th\\u00f4ng tin \\u201cm\\u1edbi toanh\\u201d trong ng\\u00e0nh, c\\u00e1c ki\\u1ebfn th\\u1ee9c h\\u1eefu \\u00edch \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c tr\\u00ecnh b\\u00e0y m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch d\\u1ec5 hi\\u1ec3u v\\u00e0 th\\u00fa v\\u1ecb. Ch\\u00fang ph\\u1ea3i m\\u1edbi, kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c copy v\\u00e0 \\u201cc\\u1eaft gh\\u00e9p\\u201d qu\\u00e1 \\u0111\\u00e0.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>V\\u1edbi n\\u1ed9i dung copy, kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u00e3 th\\u1ea5y qu\\u00e1 nhi\\u1ec1u khi t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm tr\\u00ean Google. H\\u1ecd \\u0111\\u1ecdc tr\\u00ean nh\\u1eefng website kh\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ebfn nh\\u00e0m ch\\u00e1n lu\\u00f4n r\\u1ed3i. H\\u00e3y \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi, h\\u00e3y s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o. N\\u1ed9i dung m\\u1edbi s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap b\\u1ea1n ng\\u00e0y c\\u00e0ng thu h\\u00fat nhi\\u1ec1u v\\u1ecb kh\\u00e1ch m\\u1edbi v\\u00e0o website h\\u01a1n v\\u00e0 duy tr\\u00ec s\\u1ef1 quay l\\u1ea1i c\\u1ee7a nh\\u1eefng kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng c\\u0169. B\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng s\\u1ef1 uy t\\u00edn v\\u00e0 ni\\u1ec1m tin cho kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng d\\u1ef1a tr\\u00ean n\\u1ed9i dung cung c\\u1ea5p. \\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi, Google s\\u1ebd ng\\u00e0y c\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 website t\\u1ed1t h\\u01a1n v\\u00e0 c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i b\\u00e0i vi\\u1ebft xu\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n tr\\u00ean trang nh\\u1ea5t k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm c\\u0169ng cao h\\u01a1n.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>M\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 g\\u1ee3i \\u00fd sau s\\u1ebd h\\u1eefu \\u00edch cho b\\u1ea1n khi xu\\u1ea5t b\\u1ea3n n\\u1ed9i dung tr\\u00ean website:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Xu\\u1ea5t b\\u1ea3n n\\u1ed9i dung m\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1ecbnh k\\u1ef3 m\\u1ed7i tu\\u1ea7n (\\u00edt nh\\u1ea5t 2 b\\u00e0i\\/tu\\u1ea7n).<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>C\\u00f9ng m\\u1ed9t v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c n\\u00f3i nhi\\u1ec1u tr\\u00ean internet, b\\u1ea1n th\\u1eed \\u0111\\u01b0a ra m\\u1ed9t g\\u00f3c nh\\u00ecn m\\u1edbi ho\\u1eb7c th\\u00eam nh\\u1eefng li\\u00ean t\\u01b0\\u1edfng m\\u1edbi.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>\\u0110\\u01b0a ra n\\u1ed9i dung d\\u1ef1a tr\\u00ean s\\u1ef1 t\\u00edch l\\u0169y kinh nghi\\u1ec7m c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00ednh b\\u1ea3n th\\u00e2n.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Tr\\u00ecnh b\\u00e0y n\\u1ed9i dung b\\u1eb1ng m\\u1ed9t h\\u00ecnh th\\u1ee9c kh\\u00e1c: video, infographic, \\u1ea3nh ch\\u1ee5p, h\\u00ecnh v\\u1ebd, b\\u00e0i vi\\u1ebft d\\u1ea1ng h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn, b\\u00e0i vi\\u1ebft d\\u1ea1ng li\\u1ec7t k\\u00ea danh s\\u00e1ch,\\u2026<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>C\\u1eadp nh\\u1eadt nhanh ch\\u00f3ng nh\\u1eefng th\\u00f4ng tin m\\u1edbi t\\u1eeb ph\\u00e1t hi\\u1ec7n c\\u1ee7a doanh nghi\\u1ec7p ho\\u1eb7c d\\u1ecbch l\\u1ea1i t\\u1eeb c\\u00e1c trang web n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ngo\\u00e0i \\u0111\\u1ee9ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u ng\\u00e0nh.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>V\\u00e0 b\\u1ea1n h\\u00e3y th\\u1eed t\\u00ecm th\\u00eam nhi\\u1ec1u c\\u00e1ch th\\u1ee9c s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o kh\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u00f3 n\\u1ed9i dung m\\u1edbi cho kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n nh\\u00e9!<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":9,\"created\":\"2023-04-02 14:52:50\",\"created_by\":\"570\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-04-02 14:56:12\",\"modified_by\":570,\"checked_out\":570,\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-04-02 14:56:07\",\"publish_up\":\"2023-04-02 14:52:50\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/chia-se-kinh-nghiem-marketing-online-lay-website-lam-trung-tam-cap-nhat-noi-dung-dinh-ky-768x509.jpg#joomlaImage:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/local-images\\\\\\/chia-se-kinh-nghiem-marketing-online-lay-website-lam-trung-tam-cap-nhat-noi-dung-dinh-ky-768x509.jpg?width=768&height=509\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fu